<h2 id="isi-buku-guru-kelas-ix-b-inggris">Isi Buku Guru Kelas IX B. Inggris</h2>

<h3 id="semester-1">Semester 1</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Congratulations!</li>
  <li>Letâ€™s live a healthy Life!</li>
  <li>Be healthy, be happy.</li>
  <li>This is how you do it!</li>
  <li>Everybody is always in the middle of something.</li>
